        <section id="about">
            <h2>About NutriAI Advisor</h2>
            <p>NutriAI Advisor is an innovative mobile app that transforms how you manage your diet. Using advanced AI, it analyzes your food intake and health conditions to deliver personalized nutrition plans. Whether you're managing diabetes, hypertension, or aiming for a balanced lifestyle, NutriAI Advisor supports your journey with tailored recommendations and smart reminders. Designed for everyone from fitness enthusiasts to those with specific health needs, it makes healthy eating simple and effective.</p>
            <img src="images/nutriai-app.jpg" alt="NutriAI Advisor App" class="section-image">
        </section>
        <section id="features">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <div class="feature-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Multi-Mode Food Logging</h3>
                    <p>Log your meals effortlessly with text (e.g., "100g apple"), voice commands, or by snapping a photo of your food. NutriAI processes all inputs quickly for seamless tracking.</p>
                    <img src="images/food-logging.jpg" alt="Food Logging" class="feature-image">
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Nutrition Insights</h3>
                    <p>Track your daily intake of calories, protein, carbs, fats, and micronutrients like vitamins and minerals. Get insights tailored to your age, gender, and activity level.</p>
                    <img src="images/nutrition-insights.jpg" alt="Nutrition Insights" class="feature-image">
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Health-Tailored Recommendations</h3>
                    <p>Enter conditions like diabetes or hypertension to receive food suggestions that align with your health needs, such as low-sugar options or heart-healthy meals.</p>
                    <img src="images/health-recommendations.jpg" alt="Health Recommendations" class="feature-image">
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Smart Notifications</h3>
                    <p>Stay on track with reminders for meals, hydration, exercise, and sleep, helping you maintain a consistent and healthy routine throughout the day.</p>
                    <img src="images/notifications.jpg" alt="Notifications" class="feature-image">
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="how-it-works">
            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <p>NutriAI Advisor guides you to better health in five easy steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Set Up Your Profile</strong>: Input your age, gender, activity level, and health conditions to create a personalized nutrition plan.</li>
                <li><strong>Log Your Food</strong>: Record meals using text, voice, or images for accurate tracking.</li>
                <li><strong>Analyze Your Intake</strong>: View detailed nutrition breakdowns and compare them to your daily goals.</li>
                <li><strong>Receive Recommendations</strong>: Get AI-driven food suggestions tailored to your dietary and health needs.</li>
                <li><strong>Follow Smart Reminders</strong>: Stay consistent with notifications for meals, water, and exercise.</li>
            </ol>
            <img src="images/how-it-works.jpg" alt="How NutriAI Works" class="section-image">
